<div class="help-block">
<p>

	You can find out how we use your data and how to contact us with any queries <a class="bold-text" href="#yourDataModal">here</a>
<!-- Modal -->
</p><div aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="youDataText" class="modal fade popupoverlay" id="yourDataModal" role="dialog" style="padding-top: 135px; overflow-y: scroll;" tabindex="-1">
<div class="modal-dialog popup" role="document">
<div class="modal-content">
<div class="modal-header">
<h4 class="modal-title" id="youDataText">Your data

						<a class="btn btn-default btn-sm closepopup pull-right" href="#">Close
						</a>
</h4>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
<p>The data controllers responsible for processing your personal information are Aviva Life &amp; Pensions UK Limited as the insurer of the product and Aviva UK Digital Limited who is responsible for the sale and distribution of the product. 
					</p>
<p>We’ll collect and use personal information as part of the application process. We collect this information from what you tell us, from data we already hold, from publicly available sources and other organisations we trust and from data from your device, general location and how you interact with our website. 
					</p>
<br/>
<p>We’ll use the information you have given us to decide if we can generate a quote for you, offer you insurance, set up, assess and maintain your insurance contract with us, make changes to your cover, process claims and conduct marketing and analytics. We’ll use automated software to make decisions relating to the above activities. 
					</p>
<br/>
<p>We’ll need to share this information within the Aviva Group and specific third parties. See our <a href="https://www.aviva.co.uk/legal/privacy-policy.html" target="_blank">privacy policy</a> for more about how we share your personal data within the Aviva Group. 
					</p>
<p>You have various rights in relation to your personal information, including requests for: access to your information, to correct any mistakes, erase or restrict records, and in some circumstances objecting to our use of your personal data, and to data portability for electronically provided information. 
					</p>
<p>If you have any questions about how we use personal information, or if you want to exercise your rights about your data, please contact our Data Protection Officer by either emailing them at <a href="mailto:DATAPRT@aviva.com">DATAPRT@aviva.com</a> or writing to them at:<br/>
</p>
<p>Aviva<br/>Pitheavlis<br/> Perth<br/>PH2 0NH
					</p>
<p>NOTE: If you have any concerns about use of information for these purposes, you should not proceed with this application as we may be unable to provide you with a policy. You can also contact us at any time if you would like us to stop using your information but this may prevent us assessing future claims and the policy may be cancelled 
					</p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
<a class="btn btn-default btn-sm closepopup" href="#">Close
					</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
