<p>Before you start, make sure you’ve read our <a href="https://www.aviva.co.uk/insurance/life-products/over-50-life-insurance/" onmousedown="$p.ui.page.setShowNavigationWarning(false);" target="_blank">Over 50s Life Insurance page</a>. If you’re still unsure while getting your quote, the <a href="https://www.aviva.co.uk/content/dam/aviva-public/gb/pdfs/personal/insurance/life/over-50s/over-50s-policy-summary-DA03015c.pdf" onmousedown="$p.ui.page.setShowNavigationWarning(false);" target="_blank">Over 50s Life Insurance Policy Summary</a> and <a href="https://www.aviva.co.uk/content/dam/aviva-public/gb/pdfs/personal/insurance/life/over-50s/over-50s-policy-conditions-DA03016c.pdf" onmousedown="$p.ui.page.setShowNavigationWarning(false);" target="_blank">Over 50s Life Insurance Policy Conditions</a> will be on each page and will always be on hand to help out.
			</p>
